         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne 7/8/76. ¶  ¶ It affords me much pleasure, honored and venerable friend, to send you herewith the unexpanded flowers of some species of Ripogonum; and if in the progress of your important res...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">76.08.07a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Alphonse de Candolle</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Bibliothèque des Conservatoire et Jardin botaniques, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 7/8/76.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It affords me much pleasure, honored and venerable friend, to send you herewith the unexpanded flowers of some species of <name key="Ripogonum">Ripogonum</name>; and if in the progress of your important researches I can at any time furnish material, then pray command my services unhesitatingly.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Candolle was working on A. de Candolle (1878); M's specimens from the de Candolle and other European herbaria are frequently quoted.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have been much harrassed for some time, but hope to get soon ready the plants, which according to your letter of the 22 Sept. 1875, you desired for the Monographies.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With regardful remembrance.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Ripogonum">Ripogonum</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
